{"tid":528770,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"曾志偉性侵疑雲封口4天　朱延平力挺「打死我都不信」","createTime":"2018-01-14T08:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T08:55:10.000Z","uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"56135414c954239dd0d7fc4a3002b95f38662d6a","tid":528770,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180114/640_9bd4600886111589cc74b110f22d8412.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180114%2F640_9bd4600886111589cc74b110f22d8412.jpg&h=9c973e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朱延平（前排右起）和曾志偉、邱瓈寬前年慶祝曾志偉兒子曾國祥（後）提名導演獎。翻攝朱延平臉書<br />\n<br />\n曾志偉近日捲入性侵指控，除了藍潔瑛採訪影片瘋傳，還有「中國女模教母」韓穎華不斷針對他。曾志偉10日發聲明稱藍潔瑛影片是不實信息後沉默至今，他的好友邱瓈寬、譚詠麟皆為他澄清，導演朱延平今也在臉書力挺：「曾志偉的事，只有六個字，打死我都不信。」<br />\n <br />\n韓穎華11日在微博指名道姓，稱曾志偉「不止一次性侵女藝人」，還描述自己的模特兒學生到香港險被他下藥迷昏。曾志偉尚未回應韓穎華，她態度強硬，連在加拿大的家人都擔心她的安危，她說：「有朝一日老婆子無故失蹤，或者意外死亡，大家一起討伐這賤人就是，不枉老婆子這次挺身而出。」（娛樂中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180114/1278280/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180114%2F1278280%2F&d=WedSwDmVqoHg8Gsl%2B%2F2iYwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=2fff6254\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180114%2F1278280%2F&h=a869c6f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180114/1278280/</a>"},{"pid":"cb6c25fb6433db2a40cf1ed0b5996034bbb81375","tid":528770,"uid":165875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:33:56.000Z","msg":"想低調過骨"},{"pid":"abfe28075f29f2223fb72eb2c1f6be7f2a011268","tid":528770,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:52:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16b4f52847d8dbb4a5a10d6185f80ceb63b3c9f9","tid":528770,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:55:10.000Z","msg":"實係移花接木<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}